## üõ†Ô∏è Installation

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/nya-blo/nya-blo-super-app.git

# Install dependencies (uses pnpm for monorepo)
cd nya-blo-super-app
pnpm install

# Setup environment variables
cp apps/web/.env.example apps/web/.env.local

# Required API Keys:
# - OPENAI_API_KEY (GPT-4 Turbo)
# - NEXT_PUBLIC_WALLETCONNECT_PROJECT_ID (Web3)
# - NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN (Monitoring)
# - ELEVENLABS_API_KEY (Voice AI)

# Run dev server
pnpm dev

# Build for production
pnpm build
```

